cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with neural architecture search for generative models, specifically auto-encoder based universal style transfer. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also involves evolutionary algorithms and optimization, which are relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and graphics (cs.GR). Finally, the paper deals with image processing and manipulation, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
